Mahoning County Bar Association v. Walsh.

[Cite as Mahoning Cty. Bar Assn. v. Walsh (1987), 31 Ohio St. 3d 601.]

(D.D. No. 83-12 Decided June 5, 1987.)

The petition for reinstatement to the practice of law is granted. John T. Walsh is reinstated to the practice of law in the state of Ohio. (For earlier case, see [1983], 8 Ohio St. 3d 32, 8 OBR 342, 456 N.E. 2d 1206.)

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Locher, Holmes, Douglas, Wright and H. Brown, JJ., concur.
